    • PieChart

      public PieChart​(String title, String name1, double value1, String name2, double value2, String name3, double value3, int type)
      Creates a Pie Chart type graph with the given parameters.
      Parameters:
      title - Title of the graph.
      name1 - Name of the first member.
      value1 - Value correspondent to the first member.
      name2 - Name of the second member.
      value2 - Value correspondent to the second member.
      name3 - Name of the third member.
      value3 - Value correspondent to the third member.
      type - 0 for a percentage type graph, 1 for a cost type graph
